OL,3,CSenedd election: Labour pledges 'pay
OL,4,Cboost' for school support staff
OL,6,FWelsh Labour has said that school
OL,7,Fsupport staff would receive year-round
OL,8,Fpay if the party leads the next Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment following May's Senedd
OL,10,FElection.
OL,12,FThe party says the First Minister's
OL,13,Fmanifesto pledge would expand the pay
OL,14,Fagreements and training opportunities
OL,15,Fof teaching assistants, cooks,
OL,16,Fcleaners and caretakers, and that this
OL,17,Fwould be brought about by a new School
OL,18,FSupport Staff Negotiating Body
OL,19,Festablished in law.
