OL,3,CSenedd election: Labour pledges 'pay
OL,4,Cboost' for school support staff
OL,6,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan will
OL,7,Fannounce the proposed policy at the
OL,8,FUnison union's Labour Link conference
OL,9,Fin Cardiff today (January 24.
OL,11,FIn her speech to Unison Labour Link
OL,12,FConference, First Minister Eluned
OL,13,FMorgan will say: "Our school support
OL,14,Fstaff - teaching assistants,
OL,15,Fadministrative staff, caretakers,
OL,16,Flunchtime supervisors - the people who
OL,17,Fkeep our schools running, support our
OL,18,Fchildren, and make inclusive education
OL,19,Fpossible. They are the backbone of our
OL,20,Feducation system.
