OL,3,CSenedd election: Labour pledges 'pay
OL,4,Cboost' for school support staff
OL,6,F"Yet for far too long, too many of
OL,7,Fthem have been among the lowest-paid
OL,8,Fworkers in public service. Too many
OL,9,Fare not paid year-round. Too many miss
OL,10,Fout on training and professional
OL,11,Fdevelopment. Too many feel undervalued
OL,12,Fdespite the responsibility they carry
OL,13,Fevery single day.
OL,15,F"That is not fair. And it is not
OL,16,Fright. Under Welsh Labour, that will
OL,17,Fchange."
OL,19,FThis is the party's second policy
OL,20,Fannouncement this year following its
OL,21,Fpledge to cap single bus fares at #2.
