OL,3,CSenedd election: Labour pledges 'pay
OL,4,Cboost' for school support staff
OL,6,FThe latest opinion poll from ITV Cymru
OL,7,FWales showed Plaid Cymru as the
OL,8,Fpredicted largest party in the
OL,9,Fupcoming Senedd election in May, with
OL,10,FLabour at its lowest ever point in
OL,11,Ffourth at 10% alongside the
OL,12,FConservatives.
OL,14,FRhun ap Iorwerth's party increased its
OL,15,Fvote share from 30% to 37% since our
OL,16,Flast poll in September 2025, with
OL,17,FReform UK dropping from 29% to 23%.
OL,19,FFor the first time ever, the Green
OL,20,FParty is polling in third place at 13%.
