OL,3,CSenedd election: Labour pledges 'pay
OL,4,Cboost' for school support staff
OL,6,FCommenting on Labour's pledge
OL,7,Fannouncement, leader of the Welsh
OL,8,FConservatives, Darren Millar MS, said:
OL,10,F"Labour and Plaid budget deals have
OL,11,Fbroken the Welsh education system
OL,12,Fleaving school staff overworked and
OL,13,Funderpaid for far too long.
OL,15,F"International league tables have
OL,16,Fshown that Wales has the worst
OL,17,Feducation system in the UK and 1 in 5
OL,18,Fchildren leave Welsh schools
OL,19,Ffunctionally illiterate.
