OL,17,FPlaid Cymru said: "After 27 years,
OL,18,FLabour have presided over little more
OL,19,Fthan managed decline in our schools .
OL,20,FWhy wasn't this done before, and what
OL,21,Fwill be cut to pay for it now?"
