OL,3,CSenedd election: Labour pledges 'pay
OL,4,Cboost' for school support staff
OL,6,F"A Plaid Cymru government will be
OL,7,Fcommitted to improved working
OL,8,Fconditions in our schools ` tackling
OL,9,Fthe root causes of behavioural
OL,10,Fchallenges, and improving mental
OL,11,Fhealth and well-being for staff and
OL,12,Fstudents. We will work with unions,
OL,13,Flocal authorities and school
OL,14,Fmanagement to deliver on this.
OL,16,F"We will promote excellence in school
OL,17,Fcatering, in particular, and make it a
OL,18,Fmore attractive career option, as part
OL,19,Fof a wider approach on improving food
OL,20,Feducation and the quality of food
OL,21,Fserved in schools."
